+## T001: CLI DI + WorkflowEventError + Service throws
+
+**Status**: Complete
+**Duration**: ~5 min
+
+**What was done**:
+1. Created `packages/shared/src/workflow-events/errors.ts` — `WorkflowEventError` class extending Error with `errors: readonly ResultError[]` property (DYK-P3-02)
